     F*          FILE DEFINITION                          *
     F*****************************************************
     F*==< SCREEN >==*
     FECSPW85 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F*
     FECQPPNO UF  F      10            DISK
     F*==< S/38 PASSWORD M/F >==*
     F*RGAPL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< FACILITY MANAGEMENT M/F >==*
     FMFAPL22 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< REASON FOR DIE STORE OUT FILE >==*
     FECSPP70 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< DIE KANBAN M/F >==*
     FGCQPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< DIE STORE IN/OUT RESULT FILE >==*
     FECSPL82 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
     F*
     F*==< DIE INVENTORY FILE >==*
     FECSPL10 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     F*
     FECSPP01 O   E                    DISK
     FECSPPE1 IF  E           K        DISK
