     E*****************************************************
     F*          ARRAY DEFINITION                         *
     E*****************************************************
     E                    @ER     1  20 25
     E*
     IECQPPNO AA  98
     I                                        1  100DRECD
     I*****************************************************
     I*          DATA STRUCTURE                           *
     I*****************************************************
     I*==< SYSTEM INFORMATION >==*
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM @@PGID
     I                                      244 253 @@WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USID
     I                                      264 269 @@JBNO
     I*==< SYSTEM DATE/TIME >==*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140S@TIME
     I                                        1   20S@JJ
     I                                        3   40S@FF
     I                                        1   60S@HMS
     I                                        7  140S@YMD
     I                                        7  100S@YYYY
     I                                       11  120S@MM
     I                                       13  140S@DD
     I*==< SCREEN ITEM >==*
     I*         ( REQUESTER BARCODE )
     ID#1BAR      DS
     I                                        1  10 D#1REQ
     I*         ( MACHINE BARCODE )
     ID#2BAR      DS
     I                                        1   3 D#2KIB
     I                                        4   4 D#2CDG
     I*         ( REASON BARCODE )
     ID#3BAR      DS
     I                                        1   1 D#3RSC
     I                                        2   2 D#3CDG
     I*         ( DIE LOCATION BARCODE )
     ID#4BAR      DS
     I                                        1   2 D#4KT1
     I                                        3   6 D#4KT2
     I                                        7   7 D#4KT3
     I                                        8   8 D#4KT4
     I                                        9   9 D#4TR1
     I                                       10  11 D#4TR2
     I                                       12  13 D#4TR3
     I                                       14  14 D#4TR4
     I                                       15  15 D#4TR5
     I                                       16  16 D#4CDG
     I*         ( DIE STORE LABEL BARCODE )
     ID#5BAR      DS
     I                                        1   2 D#5KT1
     I                                        3   6 D#5KT2
     I                                        7   7 D#5KT3
     I                                        8   8 D#5KT4
     I                                        9  14 D#5ISN
     I                                       15  15 D#5CDG
     I*==< WORK >==*
     I*         ( DIE NUMBER : XX-XXXX-X-X )
     I            DS
     I                                        1  11 W@KAT@
     I                                        1   2 W@KAT1
     I                                        3   3 W@KAH2
     I                                        4   7 W@KAT2
     I                                        8   8 W@KAH3
     I                                        9   9 W@KAT3
     I                                       10  10 W@KAH4
     I                                       11  11 W@KAT4
     I*         ( DIE LOCATION : X-XX-XX-X-X )
     I            DS
     I                                        1  11 W@LOC@
     I                                        1   1 W@LOC1
     I                                        2   2 W@LOH2
     I                                        3   4 W@LOC2
     I                                        5   5 W@LOH3
     I                                        6   7 W@LOC3
     I                                        8   8 W@LOH4
     I                                        9   9 W@LOC4
     I                                       10  10 W@LOH5
     I                                       11  11 W@LOC5
     I*
     C*****************************************************
     C*          PARAMETERS LIST                          *
     C*****************************************************
     C*==< ENTRY PARM >==*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@TAC5  5
     C                     PARM           P@TANM 10
     C                     PARM           P@CMD   2
     C                     PARM           P@STS   1
     C*
     C*==< CHKR03 >==*
     C           P@CHK1    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@BRCD100
     C                     PARM           P@BYTE  3
     C                     PARM           P@CKDG  1
     C                     PARM           P@RTN1  1
     C*
     C*****************************************************
     C*          LEY LIST                                 *
     C*****************************************************
     C*==< MFAPL22 : FACILITY MANAGEMENT M/F >==*
     C           K@MF21    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@KOJY  40        FACTORY CODE
     C                     KFLD           K@KBN1  3         MACHINE NO
     C*@@@@                KFLD           K@KBN2  1         BRANCH NUMBER
     C*
     C*==< GCQPL11 : DIE KANBAN M/F >==*
     C           K@CQ11    KLIST
